<text top="703" left="122" width="174" height="14" font="1">Admission of new Members</text>
<text top="739" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Report of the Committee on the Admission of New Members concerning the application of Tuvalu for admission</text>
<text top="757" left="153" width="305" height="14" font="1">to membership in the United Nations (S/2000/70)</text>
